    "Specifically, rare diseases are similar to diseases, and symptoms to signs.",
    "Depending on the context of the input text, diseases can also be symptoms or signs.Table 5 shows the distribution of errors in the few-shot setting (simple sentence + random example) under exact match.",
    "The most common error type for rare diseases is false negative (45%) followed by incorrect entity type (31%).",
    "In the case of entity type errors, ChatGPT tended to label rare diseases as diseases.",
    "For diseases, signs, and symptoms, false positives and false negatives were the most common error types."
